Mr oompapa
{{Rainbow|OOMPAPA!}}


'''Mr Oompapa''' is a well known vandal and hero on [[TOW]], well known for his [[pwn|pwnage]] of Wikipedia articles with the word "OOMPAPA!" as well as random user talk pages of people which he finds on recent changes. Eventually the vandalism resulted with the admins putting the word "OOMPAPA!" on the Wikipedia [http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=User:Lupin/badwords&diff=206353359&oldid=205339961 bad words list]. It appears that by his vandalism Mr oompapa appears to be some kind of incredibly fat Buddha that enjoys eating curry, with the word "Oompapa" itself, meaning "fat Buddha". Of course this goes to show how moronic and fucktarded Mr Oompapa is, even though the result of his vandalism on Wikipedia has generated massive [[Lulz]] to those who hate Wikipedia.

[[Image:Fatbuddha.jpg|thumb|150px|right|OOMPAPA!!!]]

==Time on Wikipedia==

Mr Oompapa in his time on Wikipedia has made many admins [[butthurt]] such as [[Yamla]] (who he sees as his arch nemesis) by repeatedly revealing his real name on his talk page, causing him to go crying like a [[baby]] for oversight, even though his real name ended up on Wikipedia watch anyway not long after. 

[[Image:Yamlabutthurt.JPG|thumb|200px|left|[[Yamla]] is [[Butthurt]] on WP:ANI after Mr oompapa revealed his real name on his talkpage]]

[[Image:Oompapa.JPG|thumb|120px|right|An example of Oompapa pwnage on a faggots talkpage]]

Oompapa's career began in April 2007, where he began messing around with [[Jimbo Wales]]'s [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:Contributions/Mr_oompapa userpage] and since the block he has used [[over 9000]] Wikipedia sockpuppets and he has been dubbed by other banned wikipedians as their [http://wikipediareview.com/lofiversion/index.php?t13012.html personal favorite]. In the same month he began mr oompapa got the Wikipedia defcon to [http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Vandalism_information&direction=prev&oldid=124680996 to level one!] when he used over 100 sockpuppets in one day until he got his Ip [[pwned]] by a [[David Gerard]] [http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:Log&type=block&page=User:81.132.72.40 checkuser], and all the hundreds of sockpuppet pages belonging to him were huffed per "WP:DENY" later on Oompapa supposedly quit Wikipedia after being identified as another vandal known as [[Molag Bal]], only to return exactly  [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:Contributions/Mr_Uumpapa a year later] and got straight into the habit of being a [[whore]] creating a page about [http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:Log/delete&page=Oompapa him returning to Wikipedia]. Around the same time [[Tibet|Oompapa]] began vandalizing [[Wikia]] and [[Uncyclopedia]] and attacked pages with his [http://community.wikia.com/wiki/Special:Contributions/Mroompapa usual style]. It is believed he spent this time off on [[YouTube|JewTube]] [http://uk.youtube.com/user/mroompapa with his profile being here], he also posted a [[gay]] video [http://uk.youtube.com/watch?v=6KYNZTXs6zM about himself] which is the most [[unfunny]] video out of many on the site.

